    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740100/extras/b76a5360a41669c3b118398727eb67f6.webp?t=1772212440\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740100/extras/b76a5360a41669c3b118398727eb67f6.poster.avif?t=1772212440\" class=\"bb_img\" width=648 height=363 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人物介绍：</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740100/extras/5f74102cd07c8c0a349e31190c3767d5.avif?t=1772212440\" width=96 height=96 /></span><br>活泼好动的小女孩,<br>平日穿着一件白色的连衣裙,<br>到处瞎逛.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740100/extras/d99855feed7249e8a4b1c5edb567f184.avif?t=1772212440\" width=96 height=96 /></span><br>忽然出现在女孩家门口的男孩,<br>不知为何呆站在那里.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740100/extras/a0109416f06afcd81ae3482135fc6bb3.avif?t=1772212440\" width=96 height=96 /></span><br>牵着一只吉娃娃的黄头发少女.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740100/extras/2954da93d788fbf80e3d40a49fd6e3ed.avif?t=1772212440\" width=96 height=96 /></span><br>女孩的妈妈,<br>平日早出晚归的工作.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740100/extras/50b4bc2296d3f5f8ad6184090933eb79.avif?t=1772212440\" width=96 height=96 /></span><br>找寻弟弟的哥哥,<br>看起来非常急切.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740100/extras/cc7d17419c3396ced51023a813d02bb1.avif?t=1772212440\" width=96 height=96 /></span><br>？？？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏简介：</h2>小女孩的妈妈外出工作了，<br>留下了独自在家中的她，<br>在空荡荡静悄悄的家里，<br>我们要做些什么有趣的事情呢！<br><br>是悄咪咪的溜进父母的房间里，<br>或者是在自己的小床上跳蹦迪，<br>还是到后院跟小伙伴们玩荡秋千和捉迷藏，<br>调戏路边的小猫小狗，<br>一起分享美味的零食等等——<br><br>也许还会发生一些奇妙的故事，<br>可能还会有不认识的人来访，<br>没准还会有神秘的访客。<br><br>或许吧<br>maybe……<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>可爱治愈的画风<br></li><li>分支向的剧情<br></li><li>离奇的展开<br></li><li>有趣的冒险故事</li></ul>",
